title: Large brick double on Clifton Blvd.
posting_body: ['First floor Suite.', 'Approximately 1,700+ Sq.', 'Ft. of living space!', 'Beautiful House in heart of Lakewood on a nicest street across Lakewood Park.', 'You get both a private front and rear Entrance to use.', 'There are two generous size bedrooms, Master bedroom with a walk-in closet, a Library/Study room,  Living room connects to Dining room via double French beveled glass door w/a Fireplace.', 'A private enclosed front porch and a back porch.', 'A foyer with a guest closet, one private generous size full Bath with a half bath in the Basement, full size modern Kitchen and a private Laundry station in the finished basement.', "You get beautiful Oak hardwood floors throughout, 9' feet tall ceilings with very unique original ceiling architectural designs and crown moldings.", 'Includes 1-private assigned parking in a private fenced-in yard with gate.', 'Beveled glass windows and doors throughout.', 'All electrical LED lighting and water softener system provided and maintained free by owner.', 'Appliances provided: Stove, Refrigerator, Dishwasher, A/C, Washer, Dryer, (3) "Hunter" ceiling Fans.', 'Rent: $1200 monthly + all Utilities.', 'Security deposit: $1200.', 'Owned & managed by CSU alumni.', '**Secured property** MUST HAVE GOOD CREDIT & CLEAN BACKGROUND CHECK.', 'Located within 1-mile of Upscale Dining, all Shopping conveniences, next to Bus line, near I-90 exit and across Lakewood Park.', 'Please call:', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a private viewing of this exceptional home.', 'All showings set by phone-appointment only.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Absolutely  ***NO PETS - NO SMOKERS PLEASE***', 'If you are a SMOKER Inside or Outside, do not contact me.', '(Leave full name, phone # and email for a reply & screening required).', 'Application fee $40.']
